{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_08_01_short",
  "title": "白石千紗 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニピの全国ツアー開始前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターがこんなに沢山……！\nどれから読もうかな……",
      "startTime": 5.8000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "全国ツアーに合わせて、ファンの願いを叶えて回る\nサプライズ企画をやるんだったよな",
      "startTime": 11.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターは逃げないから\n気になったものからじっくり読めばいいさ",
      "startTime": 15.9401240017,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3359.8759983000014,
          "startTime": 19.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、この可愛い便せんのものから……\nふむふむ……え……？",
      "startTime": 23.4767125924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？\n何か変なことでも書いてあったか？",
      "startTime": 27.8000008901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そんなことないです！\nただ、ちょっとびっくりしちゃって……",
      "startTime": 33.4713627974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "私に憧れてダンスを始めた子からで\n大会に向けて練習しているらしいんです",
      "startTime": 41.0046976566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、憧れの私にいつかダンスを\n習ってみたいと書いてあって……",
      "startTime": 48.5046979109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの方がダンスは得意なのに\nどうして私なんだろう……？",
      "startTime": 55.0713645775,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}